{"tid":1381230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"討論 水炮車策略","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:43.000Z","uid":286135,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f12662b1337f2fedd5904fda65ae5dc19576c45","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"我見到有po講話水炮車既應對策略係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拆左佢</span></span><br />\n但係拆左佢之前無疑會最少食佢一炮<br />\n我覺得主要驚既唔係佢炮既威力而係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">顏色水</span></span><br />\n所以為保護前線既手足 我建議每次發夢都好似 印度顏色節 咁搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgLDlxDjnQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEgLDlxDjnQY&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=3b9164f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgLDlxDjnQY</a><br />\n<br />\n討論下可行性"},{"pid":"f1a10e4f08791214c1e7fda2e1298a28571387a6","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:49:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6359acf7e97450bb9e160b61c5c2d1f81ef5c382","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"885847cf08a8411aa6995c9d444123d7b6a17ca3","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1a8347c591174bb4ccc8b078ee0c3f157b40b62e","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d9de1987453ff698c780dc86f2e2f9f4dda431a1","tid":1381230,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b8d90239216838635d8f35a387e46a1fd483332a","tid":1381230,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"915b31a0f9